      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA SHINE (4) is having his first look at this course. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 7 lengths (30.18) at Wentworth Park. Worth another chance. SHE'S OUR JOY (1) finished second (23.02) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th there. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. CRIMSON DYNAMO (8) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 320m behind Sammy My Boy (18.91) in a Mix 1/2/3. Was in the money prior to that. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings six times from 12 starts. Should be in this for a long way. BETH DUTTON (2) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
